  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5376438/" class="title-link">终于发现一个错误，这本书翻译的实在是太精彩了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5376438"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/nklyj2004/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1286312-22.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/nklyj2004/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">尘埃</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-06"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-06 00:05:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5376438_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  p82，霍普金斯在医学范围以外有着巨大的影响。原译文，对医学界影响巨大有误。 本书翻译的非常不错哦，自从《摩根财团》以外，很少能看见这么精彩的译文，比如p13的“衣香鬓影”，太绝了！！！！！！！！！！！

